Robin Wilson (https://github.com/robintw) is the primary author of Py6S.

Other contributors, and their contributions, are listed below:

* Vincent Schut (https://github.com/vincentschut): Bug fix for running Py6S on Linux where the 6S output file must finish with a newline.
* Matthew Hanson (https://github.com/matthewhanson): Bug fixes for various issues with setting the observation geometry manually.
